days.description:
On this day, 130 years ago, the foundation stone of the Rai Bahadur Narainswamy Orphanage was laid. The building,  located on Gangadhar Chetty Road, was beautifully restored in 2014 by @architects_mathewghosh 

The building now houses the @cinnamonthestore boutique store, @cafestoneblr cafe and a @mapbangalore store.

BLR Yesterday: Explore Bangalore's transformation through historical maps and archival documents. View maps of the city spanning over 200 years, and see your neighbourhood appear on the map as the city expands.

 Link in Bio (blryesterday.com)

Ever wondered whos in charge of your neighborhood in Bengaluru? With overlapping jurisdictions from multiple departments and governments, its often hard to know where to turn.

 Introducing cityofficials.bengawalk.com  a simple tool to:
- View jurisdiction boundaries for various authorities of Bengaluru
- View stakeholders and officers in charge for a selected location
- Access contact details of officers directly from the map 

 Open Database
The data for this website has been sourced from government websites and OpenCity. The database is open for public comments. If you spot any errors, you can leave corrections or notes on the Google Sheet. 

 A public goods invention by Vonter
This platform has been put together by Vonter using data from government websites and OpenCity.

 Explore and enjoy - cityofficials.bengawalk.com
